{"tid":2194490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「少女時代-Oh!GG」五成員 再度與SM娛樂續約","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T05:13:10.000Z","uid":251328,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1351f1801065f61341240743b0928c1a66534b","tid":2194490,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"【大紀元2020年09月08日訊】（大紀元記者曾薇心編譯報導）今日（8日）SM娛樂宣布，旗下人氣女團少女時代的太妍、潤娥、俞利、孝淵與Sunny都已與公司續約，今後公司也會繼續支持她們在各種領域中的活動。<br />\n<br />\n2017年10月，少女時代成員徐玄、秀英與Tiffany選擇離開SM娛樂，太妍、潤娥、俞利、孝淵與Sunny則與SM娛樂續約。2018年9月，與SM娛樂續約的五位成員組成「Girls&rsquo; Generation-Oh!GG（少女時代-Oh!GG）」，發行了《Lil&rsquo; Touch》。<br />\n<br />\n目前少女時代的成員或以Solo歌手身分活動，或以透過參與戲劇演出、綜藝節目、廣播節目等方式活躍於演藝圈，上月迎來少女時代出道13周年之際，還公開了「全體成員」合照，與粉絲同慶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY2gg9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY2gg9v.jpg&h=0e684a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"235d4a62f81ae59376bb00b618ee47687359f6d3","tid":2194490,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18ffd6d5c4869ac7c1182523f6857c2f1702f27","tid":2194490,"uid":323443,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"大媽時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a40b2edf8dd3068bca65076ae700fcbddb611e7","tid":2194490,"uid":56701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"為隱定公司股價打下強心針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e3357df44938ee43699ce3661960923a79ca3c","